products.description: Whether you're furnishing your first home or seeking a space-saving solution for your existing space, Serta delivers. Our conveniently packaged sofas arrive directly at your door in one carton, and they provide the perfect blend of style and comfort you've come to expect from Serta. Don't let living in a modestly sized apartment, or being on a managed budget, be the limiting factors to creating a welcoming home. The Serta Palisades collection is designed specifically for smaller living spaces, offering 61", 73" and 78" length options. With a seat depth of 20.5" you can still relax comfortably without the sofa taking up too much space. However, this means the sofa's proportions are better-suited for users under 6 feet tall. The Palisades 73", 2-seater sofa arrives in a single convenient box. The unopened box will fit any doorway, hall, stairwell, or elevator. Once in your home, it will thrive in smaller living rooms or home offices, but is a versatile choice for dorms, kids rooms, den, and family rooms. Plus, its low-profile will make any smaller space feel open and airy, giving the freedom to mix and match with other furniture pieces. This inviting sofa features clean lines and track arms for a timeless look. Upholstered in an anti-pilling polyester fabric or durable bonded leather, the Palisades is easy to care for and spills are simple to clean. 16 color options are available to complement your dcor. Please note that the actual color may differ slightly from what appears online depending on the amount of light and the positioning of the sofa in any space. Soft pillow backs, generously filled with soft fibers, rest against a backrest with structured webbing to keep things comfortable and supportive. The seat cushions are filled with high-density, non-recycled Serta quality foam, which cover individually wrapped pocket coils for a supportive core and semi-plush sit. Welcome the Serta Palisades Sofa into your home for modern style and comfort with space-saving functionality. Lounging or relaxing has never been so convenient. Fabric: Charcoal Microsuede
